<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Stripe Connect Setup Successful</title>
    <style>
        /* Basic reset */
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        
        body {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f8fb;
        }

        .container {
            text-align: center;
            max-width: 600px;
            padding: 30px;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .container h1 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            color: #4a90e2;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .container p {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            color: #555;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            font-size: 1rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #ffffff;
            background-color: #4a90e2;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            cursor: pointer;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
        }

        .btn:hover {
            background-color: #357ABD;
        }

        .stripe-logo {
            margin-top: 15px;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            color: #aaa;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="container">
    <h1>You're Connected!</h1>
    <p>Congratulations! Your Stripe Connect setup is complete, and you're now ready to start receiving payments securely through Stripe.</p>
    <a href="https://devapp.acceptmyprice.com/dashboard" class="btn">Go to Dashboard</a>
    
    <div class="stripe-logo">
        <p>Powered by Stripe</p>
    </div>
</div>

</body>
</html>
